full_text: So for awhile, I am taking a step back to relearn how to art for fun, as I used to in my sketchbooks as a kid. Not gonna even say a time of when. Where I would just draw comics and things for hours on end with nothing holding me back, which has just been me holding myself back.
full_text(utf-8): b'So for awhile, I am taking a step back to relearn how to art for fun, as I used to in my sketchbooks as a kid. Not gonna even say a time of when. Where I would just draw comics and things for hours on end with nothing holding me back, which has just been me holding myself back.'

full_text: I'm relearning cause I have fallen in a hole of trying to please people and not being proud of my stuff but it's much easier to draw things you wanna draw just for laughs and giggles. I have so many projects that should be for fun but I turned them into work.
full_text(utf-8): b"I'm relearning cause I have fallen in a hole of trying to please people and not being proud of my stuff but it's much easier to draw things you wanna draw just for laughs and giggles. I have so many projects that should be for fun but I turned them into work."

full_text: Sometimes you just gotta relearn how to just draw for fun and for yourself, and not put so much pressure on yourself to get something out that you believe people WANT you to make based on your content you usually draw. At the end of the day, you do it cause you love to do it.
full_text(utf-8): b'Sometimes you just gotta relearn how to just draw for fun and for yourself, and not put so much pressure on yourself to get something out that you believe people WANT you to make based on your content you usually draw. At the end of the day, you do it cause you love to do it.'

full_text: Fifth is to be more social irl. I don't go out a lot and I was able to do it a little bit this summer but not as much as I would have liked. I wanna hang with many of the friends I have made this year whether from past jobs or at the comic con and just chill!
